<TIMEX3 tid="t4" type="DATE">Friday</TIMEX3>'s 3rd round win was a trademark demonstration of Courier's ability  to <EVENT eid="e15" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="INFINITIVE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">grind</EVENT> his opponents into submission.&#13;
